Text: Risk offsite Team Notes Example Letter Cc Here are the notes from each of the four breakout teams and a draft letter for you to expand to send to the organization in followup to the offsite Please have patti proof the notes before sending I hope your visit to London went well I will be around most of this coming week I received your call Mary and I will talk at length today Regards to all Tom Operational Risk Offsite Jan doc
